'''Mohlajeng''' ke motse wa [[Mmušôgaê wa Aganang]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša Capricorn]] go feta porofense [[Limpopo]] ka moka [[Afrika Borwa]]. Ntona ya motse ke Mna Kose Mathekgane. Go na le dikolo tse thatro, Witlig Lower Primary, Boselakgaka Higher Primary le sekolo se phagameng, Modumela Senior Secondary. Dinaga le metse mabapi ke Kanana, Maseholong (Cradock), Motlakgomo, Reinland le Tebrug.

